-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191115%2F60263759&d=r4%2BjDf%2BCRrsm4RwUuvkwRcSEfYUahrxQZPnd5z%2FpXIo%3D&h=db77a987\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191115%2F60263759&h=389a340f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191115/60263759</a><br />\n<br />\n大部份成員相識於傘運，蜘蛛可以算是最早反應過來、明白個人力量如何在這場運動中有效發揮的一群，<strong>縱使沒有所謂「大台」，但最低限度的聯絡協作依然不可缺少</strong>，「各個小隊都係建基於大家真係現場上幫到手，留個contact，合作到咪合作囉」。在抗爭最熾熱的一段日子，每次出動前蜘蛛都居中充當<strong>協調平台</strong>，用過去經驗為包括屠龍小隊在內的前線勇武提供基本策略，盡可能減低被捕風險，「可能係幫大家plan吓，點樣行啊、點樣走啊。」"},{"pid":"bd3f632f8d10efc0152da423a2b4102bce2507fc","tid":1766077,"uid":209390,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T11:16:43.000Z","msg":"等睇尻達又出戰九東<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e6c7e06ba55d726db2d1783c5cc4ed5f4bd6c59","tid":1766077,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T12:18:23.000Z","msg":"留名睇𠝹票"},{"pid":"a6b1562006cca9c20b34da12a8267d94816e6cbe","tid":1766077,"uid":138964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T12:19:51.000Z","msg":"14年 輸 100%信大台<br />\n19年 汁生 be water"},{"pid":"76ac9719067b842fcaaebfac378179bd9839320d","tid":1766077,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T12:39:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"288397f4aaeab3561f6cbf7be670d2e954133f12","tid":1766077,"uid":63154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T12:47:01.000Z","msg":"單一政黨想霸議席就係大台，但如果所有人個協調目標係令民主派拎盡議席數量，咁唔算係大台，當中要有人犧牲小我"},{"pid":"51ed8968190cada9bd5a4a53023588465f96d19f","tid":1766077,"uid":124983,"like":1,"dislike":0,"